Disability-Adjusted Life Years and Mortality Rate Attributed to Brain and 
Central Nervous System Cancer in the Middle East and North Africa Countries.

Saeidi Borojeni HR(1), Najafi F(2), Khosravi Shadmani F(2), Darabi Z(2), 
Darbandi M(2), Farhadi K(1), Saeidi Borojeni S(1), Maleki S(1), Naderi M(1).

Author information:
