Life expectancy and risk of death in 6791 communities in England from 2002 to 
2019: high-resolution spatiotemporal analysis of civil registration data.

Rashid T(1), Bennett JE(1), Paciorek CJ(2), Doyle Y(3), Pearson-Stuttard J(1), 
